ontact HQ</span></div><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-playfair tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6 text-[#F2F2F2]\">Global Headquarters</h1><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#F2F2F2]/60 font-inter font-light max-w-lg\">Partner with Arasue Horizon. Direct lines to our investment and PR teams.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-8 pt-8 border-t border-[#162D59]/50\"><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4 group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-[#F2D3AC] transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin w-5 h-5 text-[#F2D3AC]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-1\">Primary Hub</h4><p class=\"text-[#F2F2F2]/60 leading-relaxed max-w-sm\">123 Innovation Drive, Tech City, Global</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4 group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:border-[#F2D3AC] transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail w-5 h-5 text-[#F2D3AC]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-1\">Investor Relations</h4><p class=\"text-[#F2F2F2]/60 leading-relaxed\">ir@arasue.com</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4 grou